# Cocktail Search App

This is a React app that allows users to search for cocktails by name using an API and view the search results.

## Features

- Users can enter a search query for a cocktail name
- The app displays search results with related information
- Users can click on a result to view more details about the selected cocktail

## Install and Run

1. Clone the repository or download the code files
2. Open a terminal in the project directory
3. Run `npm install` to install the project dependencies
4. Run `npm start` to start the development server
5. Open `http://localhost:3000` in a web browser to view the app

## Built With

- [React](https://reactjs.org/) - A JavaScript library for building user interfaces
- [Bootstrap](https://getbootstrap.com/) - A popular front-end component library
- [react-bootstrap](https://react-bootstrap.github.io/) - Bootstrap components built with React
- [react-router-dom](https://reactrouter.com/) - Declarative routing for React

